                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i> មើលព័ត៌មានកិច្ចប្រជុំ
                                </h3>
                                <button type="button" class="icon-btn" onclick="window.closeMeetingViewModal()"
                                    style="border:none; cursor:pointer; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color:#fff; border-radius:50%; width:32px; height:32px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;">
                                    <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i>
